00:54:07,309 --> 00:54:10,039
Jangan lihat ke atas.

687
00:54:10,460 --> 00:54:11,842
Atas? Atas?

688
00:54:13,812 --> 00:54:15,368
Apa itu!

689
00:54:17,333 --> 00:54:18,333
Siapa kalian?

690
00:54:20,417 --> 00:54:21,417
Jangan.

691
00:54:23,229 --> 00:54:24,856
Aku Lim Kkeok-Jung dari Desa Yangjoo.

692
00:54:25,383 --> 00:54:27,835
Aku kemari bertemu Wang Chi,
jadi ijinkan kita masuk

693
00:54:27,860 --> 00:54:32,195
Aku tidak peduli siapa dirimu,
beraninya kau datang kemari!

694
00:54:32,220 --> 00:54:34,740
Nona, tetap di belakangku, Chun Wang Doong.

695
00:54:36,148 --> 00:54:37,989
Nona?

696
00:54:39,517 --> 00:54:44,088
Aku kemari ingin bertemu pemimpin kalian,
