- Ya ampun!

719
00:56:18,161 --> 00:56:20,986
- Bikin frustasi saja.
- Hei!

720
00:56:38,286 --> 00:56:39,286
Seul-ki!

721
00:56:40,024 --> 00:56:41,024
Seul-ki!

