726
00:56:59,283 --> 00:57:00,283
Kakak!

727
00:57:01,943 --> 00:57:04,373
Seul-ki, apa kau terluka?

728
00:57:04,790 --> 00:57:05,790
Kalau kau?

729
00:57:06,507 --> 00:57:09,093
Maaf, maaf!
Kakak, minta maaf.

